==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Delighted
<hw>De*light"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Endowed with delight.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If virtue no <qex>delighted</qex> beauty lack.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Glad; pleased; gratified. See
<er>Glad</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Delightedly</ent>⟦br⟧
